{"tid":1546202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杯葛警察，港人職責","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T10:26:24.000Z","uid":191527,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b897fe377f9ff71c2f76ecd4aa9671035e7f79","tid":1546202,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa685705fb10056c2fa488977f12b675f8152e","tid":1546202,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2450ba33cbb84adf2e61e0772200cf8d54c467a3","tid":1546202,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4df4ab8f31fe17ef00b98e5c41544c68ea14d406","tid":1546202,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=eb1616d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"90146084461842afadeee65ee8e61f9d59084045","tid":1546202,"uid":188249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有手足即刻寫一份<br />\n不自殺聲明<br />\n交俾信得過嘅人</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不自殺聲明<br />\n本人在此特地聲明：<br />\n<br />\n本人樂觀開朗，身體健康，無任何使我困擾之慢性病或心理疾病，故絕不可能做出任何看似自殺之行為。 <br />\n本人從無睡眠困擾，故不需服用安眠藥。 <br />\n本人不酗酒亦不吸毒，也絕不會接近下列地點──<br />\n<br />\n開放性水域<br />\n無救生員之游泳池<br />\n有高壓、危險氣體，或密閉式未經抽氣處理之地下室、蓄水池、水桶等<br />\n無安全護欄之任何高處<br />\n任何施工地點（拆政府除外），包括製作消波塊之工地<br />\n任何以上未提及但為一般人正常不會前往之地點<br />\n本人恪遵下列事項──<br />\n<br />\n車輛上路前會檢查煞車部件、油門線等，並會在加油前關閉車輛電源與行動電話。<br />\n絕不擅搶黃燈、闖紅燈。<br />\n乘坐任何軌道類交通工具一定退到警戒線後一步以上，直到車輛停妥。<br />\n騎乘機車必戴安全帽；乘車必繫安全帶。<br />\n絕不接近任何會放射對人體有立即危害的輻射之場所（如核電廠）或設備。<br />\n颱風天不登山、不觀浪。<br />\n本人將盡可能注意電器、瓦斯、火源之使用。 <br />\n本人居住之房屋均使用符合法規之電路電線，絕無電線走火之可能； <br />\n也絕未在家中放置過量可燃性氣體或液體。 <br />\n浴室中除該有之照明外，不放置任何電器用品， <br />\n並在睡覺前關閉除電燈、冰箱、電扇外之所有電器開關。<br />\n<br />\n本人絕不會與隨機的不明人士起衝突，並盡可能保護自我人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n所以若網友在看完此聲明之後，近期或將來發現此帳號不再上線，請幫我討回公道，謝謝。</span>"},{"pid":"8213b15e4a531b005ddda06236269f55f710fabc","tid":1546202,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=adce1b00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"d27d6dbbfdddea46d700c5fa9cbade1cfd55a3a5","tid":1546202,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3948fb7db4756b23245f45e0936f9f624cadaea6","tid":1546202,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8be4e8cef10a15d49a444cd3faab66af9ea8dae1","tid":1546202,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大個仔</span></span><span style=\"color: gold;\">獨立必睇</span></span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大核彈</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">內容包括</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">仲有！唔止 8.31晚，仲有 9.1 凌晨！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbc1a281cb2e950f0179d009fb08e4622ee66156","tid":1546202,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dc332c6e9ba7830e4983194abfb5c02e93b6f2","tid":1546202,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11394ec6ce2a0d55413075e79018144c8f047cf2","tid":1546202,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji